## Architecture Overview

### System Components

**External Systems:**
- **ChromaDB Vector Store**: 153,459 keywords with SentenceTransformer embeddings
- **Ollama LLM**: DeepSeek-v3.1 (671b-cloud) with progressive temperature and retries

**Agents (6 AI-powered):**
1. CategoryDetectorAgent - Classifies product category
2. ConceptEvaluatorAgent - Filters subjective terms
3. QueryPlannerAgent - Generates search queries
4. KeywordSelectorAgent - Selects TOP 10 keywords (with auto-fallback)
5. TitleComposerAgent - Composes optimized title with zones
6. TitleExtenderAgent - Extends short titles (optional)

**Processes (3 non-AI):**
1. Vector Retrieval - Queries ChromaDB and merges results
2. Post-Processing - Fixes spacing and enforces locked facts
3. Validator - Final quality checks

**Data Flow:**
Input ‚Üí Category Detection ‚Üí Concept Evaluation ‚Üí Vector Retrieval ‚Üí Keyword Selection ‚Üí Title Composition ‚Üí Post-Processing ‚Üí Validation ‚Üí Output

**Zone Structure:**
- Zone A (40%): Brand + Product + ALL Specs (size, dimension, count, color)
- Zone B (40%): High-volume search phrases from keywords
- Zone C (20%): Fragrance/flavor/style descriptors

**Anti-Hallucination:**
- Source constraint (only original title + approved keywords)
- Exact name preservation (no synonym substitution)
- Locked facts enforcement (pack count, dimensions)
- Auto-fallback mechanisms (never fail pipeline)
